- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper deals with mobility datasets and their evaluation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses recurrent neural architectures and generative adversarial networks to generate synthetic mobility traces. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper discusses the generation and evaluation of synthetic datasets. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper uses machine learning techniques to generate synthetic mobility traces.
